民間外交作出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n董建華不時就中美關係闡述中方立場。今年1月，董建華以美國中國總商會名譽會長，在在紐約出席美國中國總商會的新年晚宴，提到要以特朗普入主白宮為契機，兩國既談糾紛更要談未來；今年6月，董亦曾到紐約出席「一帶一路」會議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/1944027/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E6%8E%A8%E6%89%8B%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%20%E8%91%A3%E5%BB%BA%E8%8F%AF%E4%BC%81%E5%89%8D%E6%8E%92%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1944027%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25B9%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%2520%25E8%2591%25A3%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%258F%25AF%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE&d=J2lDsVeHwS0B9dU1HFKLq7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=9f4f4f08\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/1944027/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E6%8E%A8%E6%89%8B%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%20%E8%91%A3%E5%BB%BA%E8%8F%AF%E4%BC%81%E5%89%8D%E6%8E%92%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華係usa 好多fd <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83679c2e89499c6e22528d6ae3d8aed2d8199a35","tid":931860,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T19:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/09184413/asdgasgawetgawetw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F09184413%2Fasdgasgawetgawetw.png&h=67641be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5aac1e8a4e5009b16469ccab744ad0015896c1","tid":931860,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T19:02:50.000Z","msg":"知又好唔知又好，道義上都應該去美國探吓人呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.